</span></span></code></pre></div><p>Result:</p>
<p><span class="paige-shortcode-email"><a href="" data-a="ZXhhbXBsZQ==" data-b="QA==" data-c="ZXhhbXBsZS5jb20=" onclick="this.href = 'mailto:' + atob(this.dataset.a) + atob(this.dataset.b) + atob(this.dataset.c)">E-mail me</a></span></p>]]></description>
                    

